Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I managed to defeat Dartz using the Legendary Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I got Partner and the others' souls back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Dartz offered up the many other souls he collected along with his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and was able to resurrect the God of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It surfaced along with the legendary Atlantis...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The remains of the island were entangled by the Orichalcos God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it even possible for us to defeat this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:02:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle of the Gods"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This light...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone! It is now time to lend our master our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Monsters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stare at them, Yugi! Deadbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to use this diversion to rebuild our shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me a deadbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gearfried!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gilford the Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out! XYZ-Dragon Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiser Sea Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Blader!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Valkyrian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gearfried! Gilford the Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wiped them all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Knights...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddammit! I guess it really is hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My legendary Duelists...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You cannot possibly hope to come even near the power of this God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power of this God...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...originally took on the form of the darkness in the hearts of the souls I captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you guys not hear the voices crying out from within?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones you captured...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael! Haga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! Varon! Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai and Varon... The darkness of many peoples' hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean it's growing even stronger inside here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:06:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is right! After all, it is impossible for human beings to extinguish the darkness that lies within their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regardless of how much you three may fend off the darkness lying dormant within your hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so long as even the smallest fragment exists, it can be revived at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So everything we've done up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it was in vain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie! I won't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never believe something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! Varon! He's lying, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may have only felt it for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we managed to understand each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda...! Are you really going to let everything be in vain and give up like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You shall now become one with my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me! Don't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we can hear their cries, maybe our hearts can cry out to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can cry out to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, please listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not that simple to overcome the darkness in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I've sacrificed my partner and many others in this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there is something within all of us that can never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a vessel of memories we've created that contains the bonds we share with our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you yourself... are shattered beyond repair...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you believe in that vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you just have faith in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can be reborn time and time again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With it, the light in our hearts will always shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think back, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To the people you've fought...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To the people you suffered along with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now my God has been completely resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! They're still within Master's deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... The last bit of my strength...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... give it all to you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel everyone's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They've breathed new life into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crossing over 3,000 years of time, engraved in the name of the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! The Three Illusionary Beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! The Three Illusionary Beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He brought them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He resurrected the God Cards!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Curse you, Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will erase the Duel Monsters Gods with the God of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a battle of gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it powerful enough to shroud the entire sky in black?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just how far do you intend to interfere with my plans, Duel Monsters!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shall destroy you with a single strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go on! Obelisk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God Hand Crusher!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Osiris!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thunder Force!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ra!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God Blaze Cannon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dartz!! We will never lose to the darkness in our hearts!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is... not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean the three gods won?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the souls of everyone that were taken...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:15:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've been set free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From the darkness in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's return, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brod'er!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sonia! Julien!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our souls will always...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...be with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sonia... Julien...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:16:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sonia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Julien...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amelda...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was... by Nameless Pharaoh and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that light...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's made it back to where they belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mhm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is about to be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go through there, we'll get back to our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jumpin' in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This thing...! After taking attacks from the Illusion Beasts, it's still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Timeaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Return, Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what... is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's completely different than any of the other Monsters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Any attack you throw at me now is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This monstrosity is the true form of the God of Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This makes up the resentment of every single human being on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It represents everyone existing on this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This planet and human beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as these two things exist, the darkness of heart among this planet will never vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is what this "Monster" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll stop this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't defeat this thing, the same thing will happen to the world again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it you?! Were you the one who called my soul here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally understand after receiving strength from everyone in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My great mission as the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can now feel it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:21:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To clear this planet's darkness of the heart... I must do it as Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your anger and hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will take all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will take in the darkness of heart within this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:22:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.38,0:22:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Illusionary Beasts were revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk, Osiris and Ra attacked and stopped both the Orichalcos God and Dartz along with his ambition in their tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he couldn't completely stop the curse that plagues the people of this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Yugi takes in the Earth's suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he loses, Yugi will fall victim to Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've given the future of this planet to Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Walk Into the Light"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
